Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.65,0:01:41.37,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,咦 结衣?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:42.87,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:44.12,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,这里是哪里?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.53,0:01:45.99,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,这里是真理的家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:47.58,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我来帮忙铲雪的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.01,0:01:49.80,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,那灯里也来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:50.53,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.53,0:01:53.09,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯 我正好也在散步
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.36,0:01:54.42,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.81,0:01:55.85,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:56.62,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.82,0:01:59.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,院子真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.85,0:02:01.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,那我要加油了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:02.81,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,别太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.18,0:02:07.89,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,幸好灯里过来帮忙了...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.26,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,结衣 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.26,0:02:14.79,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不 没事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.79,0:02:18.16,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,雪太重了 所以就一用劲...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.45,0:02:21.07,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,打中的幸亏是我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.31,0:02:29.23,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好厉害啊 灯里也要加点油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.25,0:02:35.09,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.37,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,安全
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.37,0:02:40.32,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:41.97,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,谢谢 结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:44.51,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,一次铲太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.99,0:02:47.34,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我想着那样能快点铲完
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:48.81,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,马上就会铲完了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.29,0:02:51.25,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,毕竟灯里过来帮忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.15,0:02:54.86,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,结衣 最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.89,0:03:09.71,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,刚才的风好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:10.76,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.71,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.01,0:03:21.97,YY-main,YUII,0,0,0,,灯里的手好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.51,0:03:28.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,是千夏发来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.68,Chinatsu Text,,0,0,0,,{\frz344.4\pos(828,573)}现在在干什么呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.68,Chinatsu Text,,0,0,0,,{\frz344.4\pos(740,480)}灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.11,0:03:33.48,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,和结衣一起在真理家铲雪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.47,0:03:37.97,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,进展不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:40.77,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,因为和结衣在一起铲所以很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.77,0:03:42.04,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.73,0:03:46.70,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:48.36,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,难道你们是在铲雪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:50.59,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,我正好带了铲子 我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.59,0:03:52.12,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,这是什么情况?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.35,0:03:53.62,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真可靠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:55.58,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,三个人一下子就可以干完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.06,0:03:58.55,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,有千夏在 如同得百人之力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.84,0:04:01.83,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,那我开始干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.29,0:04:05.65,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,难得的机会 也叫上京子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.05,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.55,0:04:12.89,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,结衣前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.56,0:04:15.71,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:18.99,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,妈妈说请进来喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.75,0:04:24.84,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,真暖和呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.84,0:04:26.74,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真理 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.84,0:04:29.58,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你们过来真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.58,0:04:32.94,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,在京子前辈过来之前就结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.94,0:04:34.57,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:36.32,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,说曹操曹操就到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.68,0:04:40.88,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,快看快看 大大的雪球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:41.63,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,快去扔掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.63,0:04:44.65,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,别再增加雪量了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.73,0:04:47.11,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.05,0:04:51.28,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,死亡面具
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.11,0:04:56.14,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,好了 人都齐了 来玩点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.95,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真理想玩什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:05:01.66,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,真理想做雪洞 因为从没见过真的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:02.79,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.79,0:05:04.15,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,哇 雪洞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.92,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好 动手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:06.74,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.93,0:05:15.58,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,雪洞里面好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.81,0:05:16.66,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,好小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.87,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,但是身体好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:20.55,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.96,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,做个雪洞暖暖身子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:26.33,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,要是完成了 我好想在里面吃肉包子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:27.71,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好有意思的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.71,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,但是能装下5个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.71,0:05:30.81,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,说的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:32.97,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,只要真理进得去也就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:33.99,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.41,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,快看快看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:36.81,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.81,0:05:37.94,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:41.39,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真是的 灯里的脖子哪里有那么长
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.39,0:05:43.36,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你真是手巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.58,0:05:45.43,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我也做个结衣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:48.36,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我才不要 快把心思用在雪洞上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.82,0:05:52.02,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,灯里死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.02,0:05:53.66,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不 你还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.35,0:05:58.33,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,姐姐 我想爬上去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.87,0:06:00.48,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,好 上去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:04.63,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.63,0:06:05.88,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我也...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:07.28,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,咦?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:09.44,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,先考虑下自己的体重
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.95,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好过分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.33,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,对少女说这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:15.64,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,快点去把洞补好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:18.66,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:22.43,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.43,0:06:24.01,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,灯里死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.73,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,完全死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.11,0:06:27.72,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不 你还没死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.86,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,好有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:31.04,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,来 真理
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.04,0:06:32.15,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,下一个是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:33.66,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你还是做了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.95,0:06:41.46,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,没想到会花这么长时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.44,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,手好沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.79,0:06:46.21,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真理没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.19,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,受凉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.19,0:06:50.88,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,进屋子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:53.58,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,是啊 万一感冒就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.80,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,诶 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:57.11,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,我要做雪洞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.11,0:06:59.18,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,要做的像真的雪洞一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.36,0:07:01.41,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.49,0:07:03.87,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,别闹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:08.00,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好冷好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.00,0:07:11.73,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,我去下便利店给大家买肉包子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.73,0:07:13.54,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,哇 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:15.15,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:17.32,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,不用 我一个人就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.32,0:07:18.62,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,你们就等我回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.72,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我带真理去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.22,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你们去里面等着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:26.22,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.70,0:07:29.94,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,结衣 我能借用下厕所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.94,0:07:31.32,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:32.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.27,0:07:39.27,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好了 被炉被炉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.59,0:07:40.60,YY-main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.68,0:07:59.02,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,京子你怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:01.55,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,被...被被被炉 坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.85,0:08:02.98,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,先冷静下来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.54,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,你是说开了被炉也不会变暖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:07.45,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:08.28,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,快过来暖和我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:09.51,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.47,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,等一下 京子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:14.77,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.77,0:08:16.56,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,灯里好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.56,0:08:19.67,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,天气太冷了 我都能理解北极熊的心情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.54,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,北极熊喜欢冷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.54,0:08:24.54,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,和京子可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:28.12,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不不 其实说不定是在逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:30.08,YY-main,POLAR BEAR,0,0,0,,我才不觉得冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.15,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:33.96,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:35.31,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,要得感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:36.90,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:38.95,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,这样做真能静下心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.82,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:46.44,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我想起以前的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.28,0:08:50.24,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,躲好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.24,0:08:52.22,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:54.34,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,躲好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:56.47,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,还没好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.41,0:08:58.77,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.21,0:09:00.38,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,京子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:03.19,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:04.60,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.83,0:09:06.71,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,这里不会被发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.71,0:09:09.87,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,但是里面漆黑黑的 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.87,0:09:11.14,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:14.36,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,躲好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:16.66,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.01,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,灯里和你在一起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:24.66,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,抱在一起就不怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:31.56,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,声音确实是从这个方向...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.54,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.94,0:09:49.31,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,发现灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:51.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,被找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.87,0:09:53.36,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,真不愧是结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.94,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,因为这边有声响
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.35,0:09:57.94,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,接下来就剩下京子了 出发去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:59.17,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.93,0:10:06.25,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.16,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,发生了这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.03,0:10:20.10,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,喂喂 别捏造了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.10,0:10:21.45,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,你难道要全部否认吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.45,0:10:22.40,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,骗你的骗你的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.77,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那个时候的灯里好可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:28.48,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,现在的我却总是依赖大家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:30.02,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:33.95,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我们也一直在依靠灯里呀 这样就扯平了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:37.00,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,有什么烦恼尽管说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.16,0:10:40.48,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,京子真的变得可靠了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.39,0:10:44.17,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我已经跟爱哭鬼的我说再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.59,0:10:47.84,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.84,0:10:48.98,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,快不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:50.71,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,不是已经说再见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:52.16,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,可是...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.16,0:10:54.23,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,但是的确很冷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:57.24,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,灯里有点想睡觉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:10:59.01,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,睡着了可不行 灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.60,0:11:02.49,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,来 用火柴来取暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.76,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:12.75,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,像棉花糖一样的刨冰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:15.36,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,现在你提刨冰有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:19.36,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,比起这个 还有很美味的火鸡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.50,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真的啊 还能看见暖炉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.95,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,你们两个人在干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.98,0:11:28.79,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,现在又看见了千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.01,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,这也是幻觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.01,0:11:33.55,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,你们怎么都脸色发青了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:35.96,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,真的是千夏酱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.96,0:11:37.30,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,这不是梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.42,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,得亲一下确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:43.68,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,这种疼痛感的确是在现实
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.68,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,{\an8}千夏酱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.14,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.44,0:11:48.36,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我也要 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:51.16,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.16,0:11:52.81,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,暖和和的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.23,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,天堂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.64,0:11:55.90,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.90,0:11:57.31,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:11:58.42,YY-main,CHIANTSU,0,0,0,,不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.61,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,这两个人被冻成傻瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.61,0:12:03.09,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,千夏酱 快回来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.03,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,被炉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.03,0:12:06.08,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,被炉坏掉...掉掉掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.38,0:12:09.42,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,诶? 不应该坏掉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.21,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,这里没插上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.88,0:12:28.89,YY-note,TEXT,0,0,0,,{\pos(1006,110)\frz6.539}好暖和～
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.06,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,活过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.84,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,在被炉里吃肉包子真是太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.84,0:12:36.47,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.47,0:12:38.02,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,千夏酱 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.55,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,但是雪洞...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.55,0:12:42.99,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,抱歉 下次再一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.24,0:12:44.63,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,想吃朗姆葡萄冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.63,0:12:45.71,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你真是突然啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:49.25,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,真想不到是刚才冷到发抖的人说出的话
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.25,0:12:50.67,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,这里可没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:53.73,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那我出去买 大家有什么想要的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:56.19,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,可以帮我带薯片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:57.35,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:12:59.79,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,海胆味奶糖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:00.42,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.69,0:13:03.10,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,海胆味奶糖和味噌味薯片对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.10,0:13:05.12,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,啊 要淡盐味的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.42,0:13:06.64,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.92,0:13:08.55,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:27.45,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不觉得京子有点慢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.92,0:13:30.12,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,便利店就在附近吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:30.92,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.94,0:13:33.38,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.00,0:13:35.58,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,雪洞做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.90,0:13:37.65,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,难道你一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.75,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,你鼻涕都流出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.38,0:13:41.71,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,雪洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.67,0:13:44.67,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,锵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:48.04,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,总觉得有些不吉利
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:49.30,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,上面还有死亡面具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.83,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,为了喜欢海胆的真理 命其名为海胆洞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.83,0:13:54.35,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,措辞好潦草
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:58.35,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,好厉害 好厉害 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:01.62,YY-main,MARI,0,0,0,,是雪洞啊 雪洞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.69,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,怎么不跟我们说一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.90,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.79,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,京子前辈好帅气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:12.58,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,我有点刮目相看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.20,0:14:14.85,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,好厉害 京子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:20.70,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,大概是因为平时没有习惯被人感谢 我感到有股恶寒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.03,0:14:26.33,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你那是感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.41,0:14:38.80,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.84,0:14:40.31,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,你看了昨天的电视吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.31,0:14:41.82,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,嗯 看了看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.82,0:14:43.17,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,其实我...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.17,0:14:44.48,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,船见同学 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.79,0:14:46.04,YY-main,CHITOSE,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.12,0:14:47.03,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.96,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,岁纳京子还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.96,0:14:51.35,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,因为感冒所以请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.35,0:14:52.87,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,诶? 没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.87,0:14:55.21,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,是不是在地上捡了什么东西吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.81,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,普通的感冒而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.81,0:14:58.30,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,她说睡一会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:02.24,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我觉得是因为昨天她在雪地玩多了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:03.75,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.75,0:15:06.78,YY-main,AYANO,0,0,0,,我还是担心新加坡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.78,0:15:08.79,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.75,0:15:14.84,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,船见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.56,0:15:16.75,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,可以打扰一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.48,0:15:19.10,YY-main,MINAMINO,0,0,0,,真不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.41,0:15:20.28,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:23.78,YY-main,MINAMINO,0,0,0,,你应该也从她们那听过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.78,0:15:25.19,YY-main,MINAMINO,0,0,0,,怎么样 考虑过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.77,0:15:35.02,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,呐 京子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.38,0:15:39.29,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,帮她带回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.75,0:15:43.73,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,买些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:45.12,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.71,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,买花之类的怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.93,0:15:48.40,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:51.12,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,至今都是敷衍的应付过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.12,0:15:53.14,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,结衣前辈怎么看?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:55.23,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,结衣前辈?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.06,0:15:57.42,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.42,0:15:59.95,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,你觉得去探病带什么比较好?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.95,0:16:01.27,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,冰淇淋怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:02.83,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.94,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,感冒的时候特别想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:08.09,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,虽然京子一年到头都在吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.15,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.15,0:16:12.95,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,比我想象的精神多了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.95,0:16:14.53,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我们可担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:18.41,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,虽然还有点低烧 不过我觉得明天就能上学了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:21.51,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,京子前辈也会得感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:22.77,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:26.63,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,绫乃也担心你是不是捡奇怪的东西吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.29,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我才没捡仙贝吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.29,0:16:30.05,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你吃了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.56,0:16:31.96,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,开玩笑啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.96,0:16:33.80,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,因为那样牙齿岂不是全都会掉下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.80,0:16:35.55,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那是什么仙贝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.55,0:16:37.55,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不如说将要变成那样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:40.61,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,被病魔折磨的时候做了个预知梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.61,0:16:42.33,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么样的梦?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:45.21,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我像平常一样过着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.40,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.23,0:16:52.05,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,牙齿突然就一个接一个的掉下来 最后一个都不剩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.94,0:17:01.66,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,不仅嘴里感觉空荡荡的 连饭也咬不了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:04.75,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,被悲痛打垮的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.04,0:17:07.46,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,重新认识到牙齿的重要性
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.34,0:17:10.62,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,这是多么恐怖的事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:13.20,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,仙贝好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:15.64,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,不 和仙贝没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.64,0:17:18.30,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,但是后来牙齿都长回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:19.51,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.02,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,这不是挺好的吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:22.69,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.69,0:17:27.02,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,理所当然存在的东西突然消失了的绝望感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.48,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,失去了才知道去珍惜的那种感觉...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.52,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,大概是这样的预知梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.52,0:17:34.94,YY-main,CHIANTSU,0,0,0,,感觉总结的很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.12,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,呐 结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.03,0:17:39.63,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我带了讲义
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.41,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:41.87,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.30,0:17:48.58,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不 那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.88,0:17:52.05,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,绫乃说学生会完事后能来就来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.67,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,太好了 会不会带布丁给我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:58.01,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那么 我们差不多该回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.01,0:17:58.93,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.17,0:18:01.28,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,京子 请多保重
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.28,0:18:03.47,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,你们要勤洗手勤漱口哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:05.10,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,都说了不会流行传染的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:08.73,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,京子 复活!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.15,0:18:10.61,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.58,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,完全精神起来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:13.36,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:16.47,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,上课的时候也吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:22.83,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,话说啊 其实昨天田径部那边问我要不要入部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:23.47,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.11,0:18:27.03,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,虽然以前也时不时来劝我入部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:30.38,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不过这是第一次连老师也出动了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.62,0:18:32.50,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,诶 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:34.52,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,结衣跑步很快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:35.99,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,没那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.67,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,我也好想运动神经变好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:41.87,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,那可不行 跑步快什么的不适合灯里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.87,0:18:43.89,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,诶? 这跟合不合适有关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.14,0:18:47.27,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,所以昨天你才有些反常啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.27,0:18:49.34,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,跟我们说出来不就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:51.93,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,因为京子发烧了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.93,0:18:54.27,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,然后呢 你是怎么回应的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.51,0:18:56.40,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,现在就是烦恼这个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.40,0:18:59.49,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,难道说你要进田径部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:02.99,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,在一起相处的时间变少了 我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.03,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,灯里也会寂寞的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.03,0:19:06.63,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,啊 那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.63,0:19:07.96,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,这不很好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.96,0:19:08.75,YY-main,ALL,0,0,0,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.10,0:19:11.31,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,就按照结衣的想法去做就好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.31,0:19:13.01,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯? 京子?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:15.29,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,我先回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.59,0:19:17.66,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,今天还有米拉库的重播
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.80,0:19:19.42,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.43,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,京子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.42,0:19:20.43,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,{\an8}京子前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:24.00,YY-main,ALL,0,0,0,,那个不是书包
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:25.92,YY-main,ALL,0,0,0,,是座垫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.03,0:19:37.85,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,京子 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.36,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:40.24,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.24,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,昨天帮我拿书包 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.24,0:19:45.78,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,没事的 反正京子的书包好轻的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.78,0:19:47.49,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,毕竟里面什么都没装
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.73,0:19:49.24,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,你上学用的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.64,0:19:53.53,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,真是的 到学校了就快把座垫放回原位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:58.96,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.14,0:20:04.22,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你不把那个还回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:05.92,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,因为好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:07.25,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那也不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.55,0:20:11.11,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那我拿回去 结衣也一起...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.25,0:20:11.62,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,{\an8}船见同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:14.15,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,田径部的人叫你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:16.16,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,抱歉 我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.03,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,大清早的不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.33,0:20:20.53,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,不 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.83,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,能去下老师那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.83,0:20:23.36,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.59,0:20:25.53,YY-main,STUDENT,0,0,0,,你考虑好入不入部了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.97,0:20:29.77,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,一直都是4个人在一起度过的娱乐部
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.66,0:20:32.88,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,事到如今成员要是少一个人...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.69,0:20:35.13,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那种事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.09,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,那种事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.87,0:20:40.34,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,果然还是无法同意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:42.98,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,爸爸是不会同意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.38,0:20:46.39,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,结衣可是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.84,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,在哪里 究竟在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.83,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,咦 京子?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:51.48,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,结衣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:53.10,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你那个胡子是怎么回事?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.10,0:20:55.00,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,田径部的事情怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.31,0:20:57.06,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,啊 我拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:58.00,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,诶?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.00,0:21:00.48,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,事到如今我怎么可能再进其他部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:03.70,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,但是没有正式得到承认的娱乐部也说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.05,0:21:07.22,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,我没有自信能成功拒绝掉 所以烦恼了一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.69,0:21:11.01,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,昨天和灯里千夏她们商量了一下真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.94,0:21:17.92,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:20.48,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,喂 京子 好难受
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.52,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,京子 快松手 好难受...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:27.07,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,你突然之间干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.07,0:21:28.32,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.55,0:21:29.88,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,毕竟是娱乐部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.88,0:21:32.94,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,4个人在一起才算是娱乐部呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.02,0:21:35.56,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,啊 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:38.27,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,好 做一份契约书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:41.78,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,进其他部的人要奉上一年份的朗姆葡萄冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:45.40,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,那只是你想吃而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:49.51,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,就算没有契约书 大家也不会离开的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.52,0:21:51.64,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:55.45,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,娱乐部是永存不朽的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.84,0:23:08.61,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,京子帮你们买来泡芙了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:10.73,YY-main,AKARI,0,0,0,,哇 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:13.31,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,发生了什么好事情吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:14.74,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,什么都没发生哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.74,0:23:16.46,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,只是京子的一时兴起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:17.87,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,话说回来 结衣前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.40,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,田径部的邀请已经拒绝掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.40,0:23:22.33,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,嗯 多亏了你们 很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:23.95,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,说起社团活动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:27.05,YY-main,CHINATSU,0,0,0,,我们学校好像要成立漫画研究部了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.01,0:23:30.37,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,你说漫画研究部?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.47,0:23:32.49,YY-main,KYOKO,0,0,0,,咽口水
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.07,0:23:33.92,YY-main,YUI,0,0,0,,喂
